mxTextCell.title: Text
mxTextCell.label:
1. The diagram represents a fortnite xp calculator
2. All calculated xp is based only on games played (no missions)
3. Experience is obtained from three sources: place obtained, kills and time survived
4. Placing in the top 20 will award xp points, more points awarded for higher placement
5. The first kill is worth 50 points, all subsequent kills are worth 20 points, up to 6 kills
6. On average, three games are being played every hour
7. The probabilities are calculated for users of average skill
